Would love to be able to sort in editor mode and have the resulting order saved on submit.  Just think, if you have an alphabetical list in a table you presently have to create it in alphabetical order and manually add rows above and below to maintain it.  Otherwise you have to hope people are smart enough to sort alphabetically (or by whatever value) each time they view the page.  Thanks.  
